INFO
  Display help pages for commands and topics.

SYNTAX
  info [<topic>]

DESCRIPTION
  With a topic name, displays the help page for that command or
  concept.  With no argument, lists all available topics.

  Topics correspond to commands (e.g. 'info census') or concepts
  (e.g. 'info sector-types', 'info syntax', 'info overview').

  Command names and topic names are case-insensitive.
  You can also type the full command name or its abbreviation.

EXAMPLE
  info                      list all available topics
  info census               help for the census command
  info sector-types         list all sector designation types
  info syntax               how sector/ship specs work
  info overview             general game introduction

